        "created_at": "2018-02-21T05:00:39.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>They\u2019re both very good and a tough call. I\u2019d probably go with 2012 as I think 2013 was just slightly better. Typically I prefer a good 6-8 hours decanting when these are really young.</p>",
