        "created_at": "2018-02-21T05:09:05.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I would decant for sure. No matter which you open, it will be a BABY. But, I\u2019m with Andy. I\u2019d open a 12 over a 13.</p>\n<p>IMO, if you\u2019re looking to lay down classic Napa CS, Kronos is a great wine to add to your collection.</p>",
